YATL - Yet Another Todo List

- YATL.ahk : original Windows AutoHotkey version (2009), kept as-is
- yatl.py  : Linux terminal re-implementation (Python), no dependencies
- yatl.js  : same, in Node - shares data files with yatl.py

Run:  ./yatl.py  or  ./yatl.js
Keys: press h inside the app for the command list.
Data: ~/.local/share/yatl (override with YATL_DIR)
